data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! --- ELEGANT SPANISH STYLE HISTORIC MANOR - Just 1 Block From the Beach and 3 Blocks From the River! Don't miss this stunning Olde Florida home with all its charm and exquisite detailing. Close to shops and restaurants. You cannot help but fall in love with the high coved ceilings in the grand living room, the floor to ceiling wood burning fireplace. This home has purposefully been, for the most part, been kept to its original Mediterranean architectural style to preserve the elegance and charm of this grand manor.  This lovely corner lot home was built in 1926 and boasts a total of 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, 3 kitchens and 2,425 sqft! NEW AC and ROOF in 2020! New inside paint 2019. Outside paint 2023. Range and AC/Heat are natural gas. The flooring has been updated to luxury vinyl but the original wood flooring is still underneath should you choose to refinish it. The unique stucco finish inside and out give this home its signature style. It is currently set up as a Tri-Plex with three separate electric boxes. The main home is a split plan with two large bedrooms at one end with a "Jack n Jill'' bathroom between them and a large bedroom off the kitchen that was at one time the housemaid's quarters and another bathroom. The spacious dining room has a wall of sliding glass doors for loads of natural light! Two enclosed porches (front and Back) with french doors, a back wood deck. The upstairs 1 bedroom apartment has a kitchenette and full bathroom that has wonderful views of the surrounding area, ocean breezes and a private entrance (was previously rented at $1300 per month). A perfect inlaw or student suite. The third unit is a separate detached studio apartment with a private entrance at the back of the property. There is a covered carport and plenty of off street parking.    With almost 100 years of history there have been many wonderful memories made inside these walls. Fun historical fact: At one time, wedding ceremonies were performed in the dining room and the receptions in the grand living room. Video security system included with home purchase.
